  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK494">
<l>eṇṇiyā reṇṇa miḻappa riṭaṉaṟintu</l>
<l>tuṉṉiyār tuṉṉic ceyiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If they who draw near (to fight) choose a suitable place to approach (their enemy), the latter, will have to relinquish the thought which they once entertained, of conquering them.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
